msgstr "पूर्ण दीर्घवृत्तीय समाकलन K(k)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ec(k)"
msgstr "ईसी(के)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1879
#, no-c-format
msgid "complete elliptic integral E(k)"
msgstr "पूर्ण दीर्घवृत्तीय समाकलन E(k)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1880
#, no-c-format
msgid "F(phi,k)"
msgstr "एफ(फी,के)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1880
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral F(phi,k)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन F(phi,k)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1881
#, no-c-format
msgid "E(phi,k)"
msgstr "ई(फी,के)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1881
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral E(phi,k)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन E(phi,k)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1882
#, no-c-format
msgid "P(phi,k,n)"
msgstr "पी(आप,के,एन)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1882
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral P(phi,k,n)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन P(phi,k,n)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1883
#, no-c-format
msgid "D(phi,k,n)"
msgstr "डी(फी,के,एन)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1883
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral D(phi,k,n)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन D(phi,k,n)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1884
#, no-c-format
msgid "RC(x,y)"
msgstr "आरसी(एक्स,वाई)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1884
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral RC(x,y)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन RC(x,y)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1885
#, no-c-format
msgid "RD(x,y,z)"
msgstr "आरडी(एक्स,वाई,जेड)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1885
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral RD(x,y,z)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन RD(x,y,z)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1886
#, no-c-format
msgid "RF(x,y,z)"
msgstr "आरएफ(एक्स,वाई,जेड)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1886
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral RF(x,y,z)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन RF(x,y,z)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1887
#, no-c-format
msgid "RJ(x,y,z)"
msgstr "आरजे(एक्स,वाई,जेड)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1887
#, no-c-format
msgid "incomplete elliptic integral RJ(x,y,z,p)"
msgstr "अपूर्ण अण्डाकार समाकलन RJ(x,y,z,p)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1888
#, no-c-format
msgid "erf(x)"
msgstr "यार्ड(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"error function erf(x) = 2/&radic;&pi; &int;<subscript>0</"
"subscript><superscript>x</superscript> exp(-t<superscript>2</superscript>) dt"
msgstr ""
"त्रुटि फ़ंक्शन erf(x) = 2/&radic;&pi; &int;<subscript>0</"
"subscript><superscript>x</superscript> exp(-t<superscript>2</superscript>) dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1889
#, no-c-format
msgid "erfc(x)"
msgstr "ईआरएफसी(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"complementary error function erfc(x) = 1 - erf(x) = 2/&radic;&pi; &int;"
"<subscript>x</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-"
"t<superscript>2</superscript>) dt"
msgstr ""
"पूरक त्रुटि फ़ंक्शन erfc(x) = 1 - erf(x) = 2/&radic;&pi; &int;<subscript>x</"
"subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-t<superscript>2</"
"superscript>) dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1890
#, no-c-format
msgid "log_erfc(x)"
msgstr "लॉग_erfc(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1890
#, no-c-format
msgid "logarithm of the complementary error function log(erfc(x))"
msgstr "पूरक त्रुटि फ़ंक्शन log(erfc(x)) का लघुगणक"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1891
#, no-c-format
msgid "erf_Z(x)"
msgstr "यार्ड_Z(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gaussian probability function Z(x) = (1/(2&pi;)) exp(-x<superscript>2</"
"superscript>/2)"
msgstr ""
"गौसियन प्रायिकता फ़ंक्शन Z(x) = (1/(2&pi;)) exp(-x<superscript>2</superscript>/2)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1892
#, no-c-format
msgid "erf_Q(x)"
msgstr "hof_Q(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1892
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"upper tail of the Gaussian probability function Q(x) = (1/(2&pi;)) &int;"
"<subscript>x</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-"
"t<superscript>2</superscript>/2) dt"
msgstr ""
"गौसियन प्रायिकता फ़ंक्शन की ऊपरी पूंछ Q(x) = (1/(2&pi;)) &int;<subscript>x</"
"subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-t<superscript>2</"
"superscript>/2) dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1893
#, no-c-format
msgid "hazard(x)"
msgstr "खतरा(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1893
#, no-c-format
msgid "hazard function for the normal distribution"
msgstr "सामान्य वितरण के लिए खतरा फ़ंक्शन"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid "exp(x)"
msgstr "एक्सप(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exponential, base e"
msgstr "घातांकीय, आधार e"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1895
#, no-c-format
msgid "expm1(x)"
msgstr "एक्सपीएम1(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1895
#, no-c-format
msgid "exp(x)-1"
msgstr "एक्सप(x)-1"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid "exp_mult(x,y)"
msgstr "exp_mult(x,y)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"exponentiate x and multiply by the factor y to return the product y exp(x)"
msgstr "x का घातांक निकालें और गुणनखंड y से गुणा करके गुणनफल y exp(x) प्राप्त करें"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1897
#, no-c-format
msgid "exprel(x)"
msgstr "एक्सप्रेल(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1897
#, no-c-format
msgid "(exp(x)-1)/x using an algorithm that is accurate for small x"
msgstr "(exp(x)-1)/x एक एल्गोरिथ्म का उपयोग करके जो छोटे x के लिए सटीक है"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1898
#, no-c-format
msgid "exprel2(x)"
msgstr "exprel2(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"2(exp(x)-1-x)/x<superscript>2</superscript> using an algorithm that is "
"accurate for small x"
msgstr ""
"2(exp(x)-1-x)/x<superscript>2</superscript> एक एल्गोरिथ्म का उपयोग करके जो छोटे "
"x के लिए सटीक है"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1899
#, no-c-format
msgid "expreln(n,x)"
msgstr "एक्सप्रेलन(n,x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1899
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"n-relative exponential, which is the n-th generalization of the functions "
"`exprel'"
msgstr "n-सापेक्ष घातांक, जो कि `exprel' फ़ंक्शन का n-वाँ सामान्यीकरण है"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1900
#, no-c-format
msgid "E1(x)"
msgstr "ई1(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"exponential integral E<subscript>1</subscript>(x), E<subscript>1</"
"subscript>(x) := Re &int;<subscript>1</subscript><superscript>&infin;</"
"superscript> exp(-xt)/t dt"
msgstr ""
"घातांकीय समाकलन E<subscript>1</subscript>(x), E<subscript>1</subscript>(x) := "
"Re &int;<subscript>1</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-xt)/"
"t dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1901
#, no-c-format
msgid "E2(x)"
msgstr "ई2(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"second-order exponential integral E<subscript>2</subscript>(x), "
"E<subscript>2</subscript>(x) := Re &int;<subscript>1</"
"subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-xt)/t<superscript>2</"
"superscript> dt"
msgstr ""
"द्वितीय-क्रम घातांक समाकल E<subscript>2</subscript>(x), E<subscript>2</"
"subscript>(x) := Re &int;<subscript>1</subscript><superscript>&infin;</"
"superscript> exp(-xt)/t<superscript>2</superscript> dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1902
#, no-c-format
msgid "En(x)"
msgstr "में(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"exponential integral E_n(x) of order n, E<subscript>n</subscript>(x) := Re "
"&int;<subscript>1</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-xt)/"
"t<superscript>n</superscript> dt)"
msgstr ""
"घातांकीय समाकल E_n(x) क्रम n, E<subscript>n</subscript>(x) := Re &int;"
"<subscript>1</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-xt)/"
"t<superscript>n</superscript> dt)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ei(x)"
msgstr "नहीं(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"exponential integral E_i(x), Ei(x) := PV(&int;<subscript>-x</"
"subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-t)/t dt)"
msgstr ""
"घातांकीय समाकलन E_i(x), Ei(x) := PV(&int;<subscript>-x</"
"subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> exp(-t)/t dt)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1904
#, no-c-format
msgid "shi(x)"
msgstr "शि(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1904
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shi(x) = &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>x</superscript> sinh(t)/t "
"dt"
msgstr ""
"शि(x) = &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>x</superscript> sinh(t)/t "
"dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid "chi(x)"
msgstr "कौन(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"integral Chi(x) := Re[ &gamma;<subscript>E</subscript> + log(x) + &int;"
"<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>x</superscript> (cosh[t]-1)/t dt ]"
msgstr ""
"समाकलन Chi(x) := Re[ &gamma;<subscript>E</subscript> + log(x) + &int;"
"<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>x</superscript> (cosh[t]-1)/t dt ]"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ei3(x)"
msgstr "ईआई3(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"exponential integral Ei<subscript>3</subscript>(x) = &int;<subscript>0</"
"subscript><superscript>x</superscript> exp(-t<superscript>3</superscript>) "
"dt for x &gt;= 0"
msgstr ""
"घातांकीय समाकल Ei<subscript>3</subscript>(x) = &int;<subscript>0</"
"subscript><superscript>x</superscript> exp(-t<superscript>3</superscript>) "
"dt x &gt;= 0 के लिए"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1907
#, no-c-format
msgid "si(x)"
msgstr "छह)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sine integral Si(x) = &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>x</"
"superscript> sin(t)/t dt"
msgstr ""
"साइन समाकल Si(x) = &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>x</superscript> "
"sin(t)/t dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1908
#, no-c-format
msgid "ci(x)"
msgstr "में(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cosine integral Ci(x) = -&int;<subscript>x</subscript><superscript>&infin;</"
"superscript> cos(t)/t dt for x &gt; 0"
msgstr ""
"कोसाइन इंटीग्रल Ci(x) = -&int;<subscript>x</subscript><superscript>&infin;</"
"superscript> cos(t)/t dt x &gt; 0 के लिए"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1909
#, no-c-format
msgid "atanint(x)"
msgstr "एटानिंट(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arctangent integral AtanInt(x) = &int;<subscript>0</"
"subscript><superscript>x</superscript> arctan(t)/t dt"
msgstr ""
"आर्कटैंजेंट इंटीग्रल AtanInt(x) = &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>x</"
"superscript> arctan(t)/t dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1910
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fm1(x)"
msgstr "एफएम1(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"complete Fermi-Dirac integral with an index of -1, F<subscript>-1</"
"subscript>(x) = e<superscript>x</superscript> / (1 + e<superscript>x</"
"superscript>)"
msgstr ""
"-1 के सूचकांक के साथ पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकल, F<subscript>-1</subscript>(x) = "
"e<superscript>x</superscript> / (1 + e<superscript>x</superscript>)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1911
#, no-c-format
msgid "F0(x)"
msgstr "F0(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"complete Fermi-Dirac integral with an index of 0, F<subscript>0</"
"subscript>(x) = ln(1 + e<superscript>x</superscript>)"
msgstr ""
"0 के सूचकांक के साथ पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकल, F<subscript>0</subscript>(x) = ln(1 + "
"e<superscript>x</superscript>)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1912
#, no-c-format
msgid "F1(x)"
msgstr "एफ1(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"complete Fermi-Dirac integral with an index of 1, F<subscript>1</"
"subscript>(x) = &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>&infin;</"
"superscript> (t /(exp(t-x)+1)) dt"
msgstr ""
"1 के सूचकांक के साथ पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकल, F<subscript>1</subscript>(x) = &int;"
"<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> (t /(exp(t-x)+1)) "
"dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1913
#, no-c-format
msgid "F2(x)"
msgstr "एफ2(एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"complete Fermi-Dirac integral with an index of 2, F<subscript>2</"
"subscript>(x) = (1/2) &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>&infin;</"
"superscript> (t<superscript>2</superscript> /(exp(t-x)+1)) dt"
msgstr ""
"2 के सूचकांक के साथ पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकल, F<subscript>2</subscript>(x) = (1/2) "
"&int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> "
"(t<superscript>2</superscript> /(exp(t-x)+1)) dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1914
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fj(j,x)"
msgstr "एफजे(जे,एक्स)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"complete Fermi-Dirac integral with an index of j, F<subscript>j</"
"subscript>(x) = (1/&Gamma;(j+1)) &int;<subscript>0</"
"subscript><superscript>&infin;</superscript> (t<superscript>j</superscript> /"
"(exp(t-x)+1)) dt"
msgstr ""
"j के सूचकांक के साथ पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकल, F<subscript>j</subscript>(x) = (1/"
"&Gamma;(j+1)) &int;<subscript>0</subscript><superscript>&infin;</"
"superscript> (t<superscript>j</superscript> /(exp(t-x)+1)) dt"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1915
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fmhalf(x)"
msgstr "एफएमहाफ(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1915
#, no-c-format
msgid "complete Fermi-Dirac integral F<subscript>-1/2</subscript>(x)"
msgstr "पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकलन F<subscript>-1/2</subscript>(x)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1916
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fhalf(x)"
msgstr "Fआधा(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1916
#, no-c-format
msgid "complete Fermi-Dirac integral F<subscript>1/2</subscript>(x)"
msgstr "पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकलन F<subscript>1/2</subscript>(x)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1917
#, no-c-format
msgid "F3half(x)"
msgstr "F3आधा(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1917
#, no-c-format
msgid "complete Fermi-Dirac integral F<subscript>3/2</subscript>(x)"
msgstr "पूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकलन F<subscript>3/2</subscript>(x)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finc0(x,b)"
msgstr "फिनc0(x,b)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1918
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"incomplete Fermi-Dirac integral with an index of zero, F<subscript>0</"
"subscript>(x,b) = ln(1 + e<superscript>b-x</superscript>) - (b-x)"
msgstr ""
"अपूर्ण फर्मी-डिराक समाकल जिसका सूचकांक शून्य है, F<subscript>0</subscript>(x,b) = "
"ln(1 + e<superscript>b-x</superscript>) - (b-x)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1919
#, no-c-format
msgid "lngamma(x)"
msgstr "lngamma(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1919
#, no-c-format
msgid "logarithm of the Gamma function"
msgstr "गामा फ़ंक्शन का लघुगणक"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1920
#, no-c-format
msgid "gammastar(x)"
msgstr "गामास्टार(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"regulated Gamma Function &Gamma;<superscript>*</superscript>(x) for x &gt; 0"
msgstr ""
"विनियमित गामा फ़ंक्शन &Gamma;<superscript>*</superscript>(x) x &gt; 0 के लिए"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1921
#, no-c-format
msgid "gammainv(x)"
msgstr "गामामेनव(x)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"reciprocal of the gamma function, 1/&Gamma;(x) using the real Lanczos method."
